    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine with its signature individual throttle bodies. This collector-grade example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS system overhaul, subframe reinforcement, and rod bearing replacement. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission operates flawlessly with a fresh Sachs clutch, delivering power to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity with zero bushing deflection, and the engine bay is free of any fluid seepage or vacuum leaks. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-division performance with a pristine undercarriage and a flawless mechanical bill of health.",
      "price": 48500.0,
