      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a factory-fresh appearance. The exterior paint is flawless, treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark in sight. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom scent; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, and every digital display and mechanical switch operates with crisp, factory precision. Beneath the surface, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a life of preventative maintenance documented in a comprehensive service binder. The undercarriage is equally immaculate, free of any debris or oxidation. For the discerning enthusiast seeking a turn-key example of perfection, this is the one.",
